Usage: reportPipeline [-help] [-netGroup <netGroupNames>] [{-spacing <val> | -timingBased  | -psPMBased } [-file <fileName>]]

-help                         # Prints out the command usage
-file <fileName>              # analysis report file name (string, optional)
-netGroup <netGroupNames>     # name(s) of net group(s) (string, optional)
-psPMBased                    # automatically find max spacing using pspm model
                              # (bool, optional)
-spacing <val>                # maximum space between flops (float, optional)
-timingBased                  # automatically find max spacing (bool, optional)